{
  "stem": "14091.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only Polish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some Russian, and of course Yiddish was my, my mother's tongue.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was affected because the Jews began-- they heard stories what went on in other places, and they became very frightened.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our life at that time was not yet affected, because a very short time, it took on a few weeks, and the Russians occupied us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this is when our lives were affected.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the Russians considered us that we were bourgeois.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It means we were the more [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] richer people, in their eyes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took us out of that big house that we lived and put this in the back, where the two small homes were.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And our house became a big restaurant for the Russian people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were very frightened, because my father didn't have any job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My brothers didn't have also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And although we had still food-- lots of food and grain and other things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I remember it was a very, very hard time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we thought that maybe it will, it will subside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the fright was never left us, because we were afraid [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that they will take us to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But somehow, my brothers, my father, managed to bribe and so we stayed, and life went on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I went to school, first grade.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And as the Russians were, they tried to-- everybody to ask to be a, to belong to their-- not to the army but to their organizations, like my sisters wanted to be pioneers or others.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But life wasn't dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We weren't-- we weren't afraid of our lives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Only after they occupied us quite for a while-- I presume it was more than a year and a half or so-- that the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
